query:
UPDATE 
    aircraft
SET
    aircraft_type_id = $1,
    aircraft_icao_type_id = $2,
    aircraft_manufacturer_id = $3,
    aircraft_registration_country_prefix_id = $4,
    aircraft_registration_id = $5,
    country_id = $6,
    aircraft_operator_flag_code_id = $7,
    aircraft_registered_owner_id = $8
WHERE
    aircraft_id = $9
